{"tid":2244574,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"沈旭暉: 特朗普 Vs 拜登：應對中國的真正不同在哪裏？","createTime":"2020-10-15T14:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T11:29:27.000Z","uid":282637,"like":51,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"a66fe966adf80f5366209781e1b8c571c899b9dd","tid":2244574,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"【突發時空・沈旭暉019🇺🇸】 特朗普 Vs 拜登：應對中國的真正不同在哪裏？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JEMNm1u_6mA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJEMNm1u_6mA&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=5e5d577f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JEMNm1u_6mA</a><br />\n堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉<br />\n16.6萬 位訂閱者<br />\n很多人認為，中美脫鉤已成定局，特朗普和拜登上台，都沒有分別。然而，<span class=\"red\">關鍵並非立場，而是手法。拜登的手法則是在現有機制下</span>，盡力和中國周旋，<span class=\"red\">卻忽視了</span>「現有機制」包括種種民主制度、西方法治、國際組織、言論自由等文明規範，<span class=\"red\">都已經被中國洞悉弱點，</span>「適合中國國情的就用、不適合的就把它丟棄」。<span class=\"red\">繼續因循，過多十年，整個人類文明範式都會被扭轉。</span><br />\n<br />\n⏺ 特朗普Vs拜登的選擇：由被港區國安法入侵的美國校園談起<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/42244898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F42244898&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=851fcb8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/42244898</a>"},{"pid":"a86cd960849a5a75a9044066951be55a6f79b9c6","tid":2244574,"uid":377064,"like":35,"dislike":13,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:27:58.000Z","msg":"拜登都好大可能繼續反華，但拜登d套路太易比中國摸透（trump就係嗰d自損八百傷敵一千ge癡線佬，中國摸佢唔透），中國一d都唔會驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444542b0fdc30a3eb46eb75bf7d8bc63b0e2b08f","tid":2244574,"uid":282637,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a86cd960849a5a75a9044066951be55a6f79b9c6","tid":2244574,"uid":377064,"like":35,"dislike":13,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:27:58.000Z","msg":"拜登都好大可能繼續反華，但拜登d套路太易比中國摸透（trump就係嗰d自損八百傷敵一千ge癡線佬，中國摸佢唔透），